## 5. 序列图 (Sequence Diagrams)

### 5.1 核心流程

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 用户
    participant A as API Gateway
    participant S as Service
    participant D as Database
    participant E as External

    U->>A: 请求
    A->>S: 转发请求
    S->>D: 查询数据
    D-->>S: 返回数据
    S->>E: 调用外部服务
    E-->>S: 返回结果
    S-->>A: 响应
    A-->>U: 返回结果
```

### 5.2 异常流程

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 用户
    participant S as Service
    participant D as Database

    U->>S: 请求
    S->>D: 查询
    D-->>S: 查询失败
    S-->>U: 返回错误
```

